titleStmt.title: Vǫluspá (Codex Regius version) : GKS 2365 4to : A digital edition

availability.p: Licence accepted by Haraldur Bernharðsson on behalf of the Codex Regius project in a mail to Odd Einar Haugen 3 November 2015.

msIdentifier.msName: Codex Regius of Eddic poems: Völuspá

projectDesc.p: This manuscript text has been encoded according to the standard set out in The Menota handbook (version 2.0 beta), at http://www.menota.org/guidelines as of 2006-12-20.

correction.p: This text has been proofread by several members of the project.

normalization.p: This text has been encoded on three levels: facsimile, diplomatic and normalised.

interpretation.p: The complete text has been lemmatised and morphologically analysed according to the rules specified in ch. 8 of the Menota Handbook, v. 2.0.

langUsage.language: Old Icelandic with Old Norwegian traits
Old Norwegian with Old Icelandic traits

revisionDesc.change:
2017-01-04
Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen : (1) Replaced a number of "Á" characters with "é", and otherwise, checked the replacement of many other character entities with ordinary Unicode characters, e.g. "ouml" with "ö" (2) Made the file v. 0.9.6

2016-02-21
Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen : (1) Revised the "availability" element in the header with a CC-BY-SA 4.0 licence; (2) Made the file v. 0.9.5
2015-08-15 Odd Einar Haugen, University of Bergen: Changed the file name for reasons of consistency; no other changes; made the file v. 0.9.3

2008-10-27 Tone Merete Bruvik, Aksis: Using RelaxN NG Schema, did the changes necessary for that transformation. Removed the use of type-attribute in expan elements, 'right align' in me:textSpan category="seg" type="right align" spanTo="fol3r.03" with 'right-align'. Made into version 0.9.2.
2008-01-18 Tone Merete Bruvik: Updated the text to Menota 2.0, which is based on TEI P5 1.0. Changes in the header.

2006-12-21
Odd Einar Haugen University of Bergen : Added a new header for testing purposes. Referred the text to the Menota P5 conformant DTD and the corresponding list of entities. Changed the attribute "pos" to "msa".
